            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "The arrow and bug buttons do the same thing they do on other Intellij project types, run and debug. Wouldn't it be wrong to change the meaning of these if that is the common pattern on the platform?\n\nAs a heavy Intellij user, I would be surprised if they wouldn't do run and debug. Maybe another set of icons would work better?\n",
